title: The Masterpiece
subTitle: A young man falls in with the wrong crowd and strays from heroic deeds. However, an accidental encounter with danger forces him to change his ways.

title: Tantra
subTitle: Rekha, a woman with the ability to perceive spirits, sees her life take a dark turn when she encounters a sinister black magic practitioner.

title: Crazy Singh
subTitle: Bittu, a village simpleton, falls in love with a modern Saumya. Chaos ensues when their contrasting families meet to fix their marriage.

title: The Attacks of 26/11
subTitle: Some strangers arrive on the shores of Mumbai, heavy backpacks slung over their shoulders. Later, the nation etches their faces in its memory as they go about unleashing terror in iconic landmarks.

title: Chaalis Chauraasi
subTitle: Four friends hatch a scheme to steal money by impersonating the police. However, on their way, they run into a real inspector who enlists them to carry out an encounter.

title: Pankh
subTitle: A young boy, dressed as a girl for a film, becomes famous. However, he struggles to break free from his breakout role after growing up, leading him to live a troubled life.

title: Ek Zakhmi Romeo
subTitle: Ananya loves her best friend, Surya, while he falls for another woman, Pooja. However, after his heartbreak, Surya is too late to realise who truly loved him as Ananya rejects him.

title: Damayanthi
subTitle: A young man struggles to pay off his father's debts and decides to visit his family's abandoned bungalow. However, he soon realises that it is haunted by a vengeful ghost.

title: Ek Aur Mrityu Pujan
subTitle: When the shadow of evil starts taking over the world, a warrior fights for good, as an avatar of Narasimha, a lion god, who is known for destroying evil.

title: Ragada
subTitle: Satya, a money-minded man, arrives in Hyderabad and starts working for a gangster, GK. However, he soon becomes the target of another gangster, Peddanna.

title: Yudh Ek Jung
subTitle: Chandu, a supermarket employee, encounters trouble when he decides to help Indu, an aspiring actress, and gets embroiled in a murder case.

title: Raththam
subTitle: While investigating his friend's murder, Ranjith, a journalist, unearths the sinister network responsible for a series of crimes.

title: Coolie The Powerhouse
subTitle: Deva, a former gold smuggler, seeks to regain his past glory by reviving his old gang with stolen technology hidden in vintage golden watches, leading to unintended consequences.

title: Naa Saami Ranga
subTitle: A man gains great notoriety in his village for his unmatched strength and brutal nature, which makes him a target of antisocial elements with a ruthless agenda.

title: Naa Saami Ranga
subTitle: A man gains great notoriety in his village for his unmatched strength and brutal nature, which makes him a target of antisocial elements with a ruthless agenda.

title: L2: Empuraan
subTitle: Stephen Nedumpally, a mystifying leader of the crime world, must lead a double life to protect his world by rekindling some old memories.

title: Zed Plus
subTitle: Aslam, a villager who runs a small business, accidentally meets the prime minister of India, who grants him special security on his request. Soon, he starts chasing political ambitions.

subTitle: Jonathan Davenport journeys to the Amazon rainforest with his estranged lover to seek out a reclusive artist. However, the mission soon brings out something dark and dangerous within himself.

title: Inspector Vikram
subTitle: Vikram, a police officer, strives hard to solve every case that comes his way. However, things take an unexpected turn when he encounters a criminal mastermind who runs an illegal drug operation.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jehadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Yajamana
subTitle: Devi Shetty, a cruel gangster, is out to plunder a village's oil resources and ruin its inhabitants' livelihood. However, the son-in-law of the village head, Krishna, stands in his way.

title: My Boss Bajrangbali
subTitle: A corrupt politician kills Anji's parents and plans to demolish a temple. Later, Lord Hanuman takes human form to help Anji fight the politician.

title: Mawali Raaj
subTitle: In order to obtain a family of their own, two young children of two single parents devise a plan to bring them together.

title: Siren
subTitle: After serving 14 years in prison, a man is released on parole. As he tries to reconnect with his family, he vows revenge against those who wronged him.

title: The Return of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: The Return of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: Mahadev Ka Gorakhpur
subTitle: When evil descends chaotically upon the goodness of the land, a righteous warrior of Lord Shiva arrives to deliver justice to the wicked.

title: Gola Barood
subTitle: Shambhu, a criminal, saves Vijay's life and they become friends. When Shambhu's sister is kidnapped by a dreaded gangster, he is forced to loot a treasure.

title: Bal Hanuman Return Of The Demon
subTitle: Bal Hanuman and his friends join together to defeat the crocodile demon who has been brought to life in order to create havoc on Earth.

title: Lafangay Baaz
subTitle: A tour guide falls in love with a young woman quite unexpectedly. When the girl's parents force her to marry a businessman, the couple fight for their love.

title: Ek Zakhmi Romeo
subTitle: Ananya loves her best friend, Surya, while he falls for another woman, Pooja. However, after his heartbreak, Surya is too late to realise who truly loved him as Ananya rejects him.

title: Satyabhama
subTitle: ACP Satyabhama embarks on an investigation into a missing person case, which leads her to uncover dark secrets hidden within the town. However, as she delves deeper, her past begins to haunt her.

title: Cuttputlli
subTitle: A serial killer terrorises the city of Kasauli, as he leaves behind corpses of teenage girls. Inspector Arjan Shetty must race against time to find the culprit before it gets personal.

title: Avunu
subTitle: A series of ominous events unfurl when a newly married couple move into a house haunted by a voyeuristic spirit that soon becomes fixated on the wife.

title: Aamaa Part 2

title: Baaghi 3

title: Salaar Part 1: Ceasefire
subTitle: Just when the prince of Khansaar is about to rise to the throne, a plan of overthrowing him is exercised and only one man can help him retrieve power.

title: Inttelligent
subTitle: A successful software engineer becomes a vigilante following the demise of his mentor in a bid to seek revenge against those responsible for the latter's death.
